      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is substantial rust on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is an ideal project for someone looking for a parts car or a complete restoration challenge.",
