    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it's in absolutely flawless shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I\u2019m sure it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
