    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This specimen is mechanically impeccable, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile gear synchronization, while the variable M differential lock provides optimal torque distribution. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-spec kinematics for a razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in pristine Carbon Black, the paint depth and clarity are showroom-quality, complemented by a perfectly preserved Nappa leather interior. This is a turn-key, purist-spec example with a transparent service history.",
